{"id": "1520817187714236505", "channel_id": "1520664438456324096", "author_id": "735137568307282011", "author_name": "reya.li", "content": "It's a really strange balance change and I think it sets a bad precedent as well. Personally I would be open to the idea of some nerfs if they were addressing things which caused serious practical imbalance in the game.\n\nBut I mean in this case, the GMurphy with Miryam wheel interaction in Madness HSR/Train mode to get a large amount of additional Crit DMG% (due to GMurphy's uncapped Enlighten 2 talent) is used by at most 10 people on Earth! It seems like an unnecessary severe target nerf as opposed to something that benefits the game at all. I can't speak for them, but if I was one of the tiny number of people who invested into Miryam's wheel for this purpose, I'd be really annoyed. I think they should have the option to be refunded for it.\n\nI suppose it's also a great wheel in Phantasmal Dive for GMurphy too, but let's be real, she's still going to be by far the best character in that mode and clear in 3 turns, just with a different Wheel.", "timestamp": "2026-06-28T15:44:32.968000+00:00", "thread_id": "1520664438456324096", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-28T15:47:18.210000+00:00"}
