{"id": "1520817662677225527", "channel_id": "1520664438456324096", "author_id": "735137568307282011", "author_name": "reya.li", "content": "For people's reference, I marked where Miryam Wheel was used in the HSR mode's leaderboard which I think illustrates how niche of a target nerf this is.", "timestamp": "2026-06-28T15:46:26.208000+00:00", "thread_id": "1520664438456324096", "reactions": [{"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}, {"emoji": "🔥", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1520817662249275506", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1152753, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1520664438456324096/1520817662249275506/image.png?ex=6a429352&is=6a4141d2&hm=010531105df9dc19f64383aad1e220b0bb7c86a38f5c7f0c7b53bdf1a5c25ec4&"}]}
